---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Lit Components - Home" showSidebar={false}>
	<div class="py-12 space-y-6">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Introduction</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
            A lightweight, customizable component library built with Lit and Tailwind CSS.
        </p>
        
        <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
            <p>
                This library provides a set of reusable UI components that can be used in any web project. 
                They are built as standard Web Components, making them compatible with React, Vue, Svelte, Angular, or vanilla HTML/JS.
            </p>
            
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>Built with <strong>Lit</strong> for performance and standard compliance.</li>
                <li>Styled with <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> for easy customization.</li>
                <li><strong>Accessible</strong> WAI-ARIA compliant patterns.</li>
                <li><strong>Lightweight</strong> with minimal dependencies.</li>
                <li><strong>Framework Agnostic</strong> works everywhere.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4">
                <a href="/components/button" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 h-10 px-4 py-2">
                    Browse Components
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/your-repo/lit-components" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 border border-input bg-background hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-10 px-4 py-2">
                    GitHub
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
